Class Island

  • java.lang.Object
    • Island
  • public class Island
extends java.lang.Object
    An island is part of a FIRE resort.Each island has a name, a luxury rating and a capacity which represents the maximum number of people(passes) who can be on the island at any one time. Each island must maintain a list of all people (passes) currently on the island. These lists are updated whenever passes enter or leave an island,so that it is always possible to say which passes are on the island
